            provision of the Benefits to the Member (“Local Contract”);
            and (d) the Local Contract will be governed by the local laws
            and venue applicable to that MO Hotel supplying the Benefits
            to the Member.

         2. A list of the currently available Benefits can be found at
            www.mandarinoriental.com/fans-of-mo/terms-conditions/benefits.
