            the Member.

         5. Members will only be entitled to receive the Benefits if they
            have clearly identified themselves to the MO Hotel front desk
            staff at check-in and provided their Membership ID number.

         6. Some Benefits may not be available at all MO Hotel locations.

         7. Unless otherwise stated, the Benefits cannot be used in
            conjunction with any other promotions or discounts.

         8. If the Benefit provided by a MO Hotel includes the provision
            of internet access at the MO Hotel, then the Member will be
