General Terms & Conditions and Privacy Policy for the "Fans of M.O.
Programme"

   [ ]

   I have read and agree to MOHG's Privacy Policy, including MOHG
   collecting, retaining and processing my name, transaction data, contact
   details, preferences (including sensitive data e.g. food allergies,
   medical conditions, where relevant) and demographics (collectively,
   “Personal Data”) from the information I provide to MOHG and/or
   otherwise collected at MOHG properties, in order for MOHG to inform
   and/or provide me with MOHG’s products and services and allow MOHG to
   proceed with the anonymization of my data for analytics and related
   marketing activities. In doing so, my Personal Data will be shared with
   MOHG’s global network of companies and its service providers, which may
   be transferred to, processed in and stored at a country outside my
   country of residence (including outside the EU/EEA).

   To unsubscribe from marketing communications or to correct/delete your
   Personal Data, contact MOHG at data-protection@mohg.com. By
   unsubscribing from marketing or deleting your Personal Data, your Fans
   of M.O. Programme membership will terminate.

   By clicking "Join Now", I consent to the MOHG General Terms &
   Conditions.
   Join Now

The Benefits of Joining

   As a Fan of M.O., we offer you the convenience of faster booking,
   complimentary WiFi and exclusive members-only offers from our hotels
   and partners around the world. Whenever you book online through our
   website, we invite you to choose two additional privileges.

PRIVILEGES FOR ALL FANS OF M.O.

Complimentary WiFi

   Stay connected throughout your stay.

Welcome Amenity

   Something special awaits.

Members Only Offers

   Exclusive offers chosen with you in mind.

Partner Benefits

   Access to a variety of exclusive benefits and offers from select
   partners.
   Swipe to See More

FANS WHO BOOK ONLINE MAY SELECT TWO ADDITIONAL PRIVILEGES SUCH AS:

   Early Check-in

Early Check-in

   Start your stay a little earlier, from 12pm.
   Late Check-out

Late Check-out

   Stay a little longer. We would be more than delighted to extend your
   stay with us until 4pm.
   Daily Breakfast

Daily Breakfast

   We want to give you the best start to each day, therefore breakfast is
   on us.
   Dining or Spa Credit

Dining or Spa Credit

   Indulge yourself with a credit towards a relaxing spa treatment or an
   innovative dining experience.
   Room Upgrade

Room Upgrade

   When you visit, we'll do our very best to give you the best.
   Streaming WiFi

Streaming WiFi

   Download, play games and stream as much as you wish.
   Celebratory Treat

Celebratory Treat

   Let us help you make your celebration memorable.
   Pressing Services

Pressing Services

   We'll make sure you look sharp, with complimentary pressing or
   laundering of your favourite item.

